item.title: Getting started with youtube
item.description: Installation or Setup # To begin using YouTube, just head over to youtube.com and use the search bar on the top of the page to find the required subject. Alternatively, you could just browse the home page. On this page, you can search the popular and trending videos, from Music, to gaming. If you wish to participate with comments, likes, playlists, or even your own videos, you need a Google account.
